# MICRO-INTERACTIONS & 60-FPS ANIMATION (PREMIUM ONLY)
- Standard: CSS-only for simple transitions, JS (Intersection Observer) for scroll. 
- Performance: Use ONLY `transform` and `opacity`. Strict 60-FPS. No `layout shifts` or `paint triggers`.
- Interactions:
  - Scroll: Smooth cascade `fade-in-up` for sections/cards.
  - "Transformation" Block: Custom smooth slider (Before/After) or cross-fade transition on button click.
  - Premium Details: Magnetic hover effects for main buttons, subtle parallax for images (bio/process).
- Aesthetics: High-end easing (cubic-bezier 0.4, 0, 0.2, 1). No bouncy or aggressive motions.
